StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.INSERTSUBJECT(pSubjectName IN VARCHAR2, pCredit IN NUMBER,&lt;br/&gt;pSubjectPrerequisites IN VARCHAR2, pIDPerson IN NUMBER) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; INSERT INTO Subject_table&lt;br/&gt; VALUES(Subject_obj(sequenceSubjectID.Nextval, pSubjectName, pCredit, pSubjectPrerequisites, pIDPerson));&lt;br/&gt; COMMIT;&lt;br/&gt;END insertSubject;
